Open Vote
Open Vote is an open source project that will have its final license determined sometime in the future.

The purpose of open vote is to create an easy to use and free as in beer real-time voting system to enable group participation for civic and educational activities.  Open-Vote will will consist of an open source project and a hosted service that will offer a free version for educational and non-profit groups.  The hosted service may be monitized in some way in order to pay for overhead.  But the true intention of the service is to be as free and flexible as possible.
